snippet.title: Stardust Exile Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
1.0 Release trailer (November 2024): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BM7SILK8dLk

Stardust Exile is a space RTS set in the Milky Way galaxy, containing currently known stars and exoplanets with their real characteristics. The remaining stars and planets are procedurally generated based on currently known data, totaling 200,418,611,014 star systems.

Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1858900/Stardust_Exile/

Video Music: NEFFEX - The Itch (Instrumental)
